title: Sudan Gasoline Prices
description: Gasoline Prices in Sudan decreased to 0.92 USD/Liter in October from 1.30 USD/Liter in September of 2022. Gasoline Prices in Sudan averaged 0.88 USD/Liter from 2020 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 2.30 USD/Liter in January of 2021 and a record low of 0.12 USD/Liter in January of 2020. This page provides - Sudan Gasoline Prices- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: The Ministry of Oil and Gas, Sudan
